content: During the first nine months of this year, we've invested just over $1 billion on new rental equipment that's up from $809 million for the first nine months of last year. On the expansion front, for the nine months of this year, we've invested just over $1 billion in real estate acquisitions along with the development of self-storage and U-Box warehouses, that's up from $783 million last year. So -- and also availability, I'll be a little wrong, but we have roughly 2,000 more trucks down for maintenance today, then we did a year ago, because you've seen as you probably know from just maintaining your own vehicle, there's a whole bunch of  to it, and then sequel, you got to get it to maintenance and you got to get it back out of maintenance.
